{
  "text": "All analyses were conducted in SAS, version 9.3 (SAS Institute Inc). To reduce survey response bias, data were weighted for nonresponse based on age, sex, race/ethnicity, and insurance. Poststratification weights were used to adjust for the Medicaid oversample in North Carolina's evaluation to appropriately reflect the overall sample eligible for the evaluation. Weights were computed using a raking macro [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "6733788"
